original_title: Jimeoin and Bob's Cooking Show: Live at the Famous Spiegeltent
overview: Jump out of the frying pan and into the fire with this hilarious show based around cooking, kitchens and everything unrelated! Filmed live from The Famous Spiegltent, enjoy a one hour show with Bob and Jimeoin as they prepare dishes that no one would want at the table when they get home.
title: Jimeoin and Bob's Cooking Show: Live at the Famous Spiegeltent
